description:
Touring: DEEP
MantaBUS is a nonprofit, nonviolent sentient organism which provides tours and transportation to all within the weight limit, and protects its patrons as they embark on a scenic voyage. 

Please see the GUIDE for additional info. (bio)
about:
Typical times of MantaBUS operation are 5:30 - 11:00.
GUIDE: 
- Remain seated at all times
- Become a specified animal if requested
- Spamming is not tolerated
Have a safe and scenic trip!
Attempts to disable the MantaBUS are seen as acts of vandalism.
